''AKA IX, IXP''

An [[Internet Exchange Point]] is the physical infrastructure through which [[Internet Service Providers|Internet Service Provider]] and [[Content Delivery Networks|Content Delivery Network]] exchange Internet traffic between their [[Autonomous Systems|Autonomous System (Internet)]].

